- 'Mandatory' refers to questions where the `required` field is set to 1;
- 'Multiple-choice' refers to questions where the `question_type` is 'multiple choice'.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT q.question_id) AS distinct_questions
FROM questions q
JOIN survey_access sa ON q.survey_id = sa.survey_id;

